MetaDataGeneric.title: Fitpass | One pass fits all
MetaDataGeneric.description: Fitpass is a prominent brand in the field of sports and recreation, founded in 2014 in Serbia. The Fitpass concept brought a revolution to fitness by allowing users to access a wide range of sports facilities and activities across the country with a single membership.
